<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM4.6">
<l>aṟṟa vaṉmaru tammuṟi yanaṭai</l>
<l>kaṟṟa vaṉkañ caṉaivañ caṉaiyiṉāl</l>
<l>ceṟṟa vaṉtika ḻummatu raippatik</l>
<l>koṟṟa vaṉvaril kūṭiṭu kūṭalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O circle! [You] be joined if</l>
<l rend="indent">He who decided [to make me],</l>
<l rend="indent">He who learnt to walk in such a way that the Arjuna trees broke,</l>
<l rend="indent">He who defeated Kaṃsa through deceit,</l>
<l rend="indent">the King of the shining city of Mathurā</l>
<l>comes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
